for the donor and the beneficiary.

570
00:39:11,098 --> 00:39:12,266
I see.

571
00:39:14,393 --> 00:39:17,063
Goodness, I'm so brazen.

572
00:39:18,314 --> 00:39:20,274
I'm starting to wish I could live longer.

573
00:39:22,651 --> 00:39:25,738
But in your daughter's case,

574
00:39:26,447 --> 00:39:28,407
she has to get a checkup first.

575
00:39:28,991 --> 00:39:30,701
This is a hereditary disease.

576
00:39:33,454 --> 00:39:34,497
