594
00:40:40,271 --> 00:40:44,191
Goodness, I am a huge disaster
in my daughter's life.

595
00:40:45,609 --> 00:40:47,862
The numbers show
that you won't be able to survive

596
00:40:47,945 --> 00:40:49,822
unless you get a transplant surgery.

597
00:40:50,489 --> 00:40:53,659
