00:50:31,319 --> 00:50:32,404
I'm sorry.

713
00:50:33,572 --> 00:50:34,990
I was too late.

714
00:50:47,753 --> 00:50:51,339
I had bad taste in men.

715
00:50:52,466 --> 00:50:56,094
